<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَنَفُّسٍ يَسِيرَيْنِ، أَوِ اخْتِلَاجٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ طَلَبَ الوَرَثَةُ القِسْمَةَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وُقِفَ لَهُ الأَكْثَرُ مِنْ إِرْثِ ذَكَرَيْنِ أَوْ أُنْثَيَيْنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَيُدْفَعُ لِمَنْ لَا يَحْجُبُهُ إِرْثُهُ كَامِلاً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَلِمَنْ يَنْقُصُهُ اليَقِينُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِذَا وُلِدَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- أَخَذَ نَصِيبَهُ، وَرُدَّ ظظ مَا بَقِيَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ أَعْوَزَ شَيْئاً:</span> رَجَعَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَمَنْ قَتَلَ مُوَرِّثَهُ، وَلَوْ بِمُشَارَكَةٍ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ سَبَبٍ:</span> لَمْ يَرِثْهُ إِنْ لَزِمَهُ قَوَدٌ، أَوْ دِيَةٌ، أَوْ كَفَّارَةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَلَا يَرِثُ رَقِيقٌ، وَلَا يُورَثُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَيَرِثُ مُبَعَّضٌ، وَيُورَثُ،<span class="c5"> وَيَحْجُبُ:</span> بِقَدْرِ حُرِّيَّتِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>